", "last_comment_created": 1774601216889, "content": "<p>Australia has about 9 days of fuel left and New Zealand is basically using rickshaws for deliveries.   China is the main supplier for Jet A1 fuel for Australia and China cut them off due to their own lack of fuel.</p>\n<p>Australia is the 2nd biggest exporter of coal in the world.  That said, it can only export if they can get the coal to ship yard loading facilities.  It takes diesel fuel to run the trains and that is in low supply also.  Australia and New Zealand are a bunch of sissy dumbasses for not having strategic oil reserves.</p>\n<p>Now Australia is looking to the US for help.  LOL.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 12, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2037228260497482187", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZ3dxaqK", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 86, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8515614, "raw_content": "", "author": "Crucible", "created": 1774558495919, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Vermino", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZ3dxaqK.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/TRHLofficial/status/2037228260497482187?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Question for Crazy Uncle Huckabee: Who or what is \"We\"? And why is \"We\" trying to 'program' (his words) younger generations? This sounds like communism. ", "last_comment_created": 1774564911637, "conte